show.description: Shivi, a strong-willed woman with emotional scars, and Avi, a billionaire entangled in family power games. What begins as a pretend relationship spirals into a complex web of emotional conflicts, buried secrets, and shifting loyalties. As personal agendas collide, both must navigate truth, trust, and their evolving connection.
